snippet.title: Astria Ascending - The Fated Eight Trailer - Nintendo Switch | E3 2021
snippet.description:
Explore a vast world on the brink of chaos and ascend to your fate to save the world when Astria Ascending, a hand-drawn, turn-based JRPG comes to Nintendo Switch on 9/30!

Learn more here: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/astria-ascending-switch/
